	<!-- message -->
	<p>I think you were pretty inconsiderate not to have informed the group as soon as you realised you would have to leave in 30 minutes.  You said you got the raid call on the way to the dungeon so that would have been the time to let them know, then they could have replaced you if they felt they needed to.  If they then decided to carry on anyway and see if they could finish in that time then fair enough, but give them some warning.</p>
	
	
	
