	<p>With 30 minutes till the raid, i would try to finish the group, show up to raid late.<br />
<br />
You made a commitment to the group, you should follow through. If its a night that your guild might raid, dont do ldon. Doesnt give your guild a good rep, if people think you will bail on them at a moments notice.<br />
<br />
Its easy to show commitment to the guild, and a raid where you might get loot. Its tougher to show commitment to random people in an ldon group. Which do you think takes a bit more of a hard decision, and earns you more karma?)</p>
	
	
	
	
	
